snippet.title: UNBOXED: Quantum Break: Timeless Collector's Edition
snippet.description:
Thomas from Remedy dives deep into the collector's edition of Quantum Break. This very special showcase-piece includes the PC DX11 version of Quantum Break and comes with an abundance of collectables:

• Premium packaging
• 5 Game Discs (one-time Steam key redemption required)
• Making of Blu-Ray
• Making of Book
• 1 Soundtrack CD (Audio-CD)
• 2 Posters
• Quickstart Guide

https://www.amazon.com/Quantum-Break-Timeless-Collectors-PC/dp/B01K7SG0EY/
